âœ… 8. Summary: How DDD Helps Here
Separation of responsibility â†’ No mixed logic in API or UI.

Team autonomy â†’ UI team works with clean APIs per context.

Scalability â†’ Order and Statement APIs evolve independently.

Clarity â†’ Everyone (even non-tech folks) uses the same vocabulary.
